    <item>
      <title>印度备受争议的公民法遭到反对派猛烈抨击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/india-enacts-controversial-citizenship-law-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度实施了一项基于宗教的法律，该法律被视为对穆斯林的歧视，引发了反对党的强烈反对，他们指责总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政府在选举前几周使选民两极分化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/india-enacts-controversial-citizenship-law-ahead-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 14:38:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
